r s BC-FBN-LeBRETON-WRITETHR     09-12 0820
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FBN-LeBRETON-WRITETHRU-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
OLD GUARD RODE SILENT ROCKET IN RETURN TO PREVIOUS GLORIES 
EDITORS: FIXES HEADLINE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By GIL LeBRETON 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   LANDOVER, Md. _ He was gone in a blink, like a lightning bolt in
the night.
</P>
<P>
   Raghib ``Rocket'' Ismail's business was done. His presence duly
noted. His impact upon the day's events stunningly established.
</P>
<P>
   And his locker was empty.
</P>
